{"tid":2160408,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"測掌欠準 無人看守  街市探熱器虛設","createTime":"2020-08-17T02:38:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T02:44:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bc161b3e59495bca8edb4cead3871abd6ab9cab9","tid":2160408,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T02:38:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200817/QIT6AHBRJBGQHNFQPSUTNCKW64/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200817%2FQIT6AHBRJBGQHNFQPSUTNCKW64%2F&d=F9sYfJh4wRYjdPScc1OpRiLieoVo5Z%2Bt8AyiqwqBN0Y%3D&h=6762f070\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200817%2FQIT6AHBRJBGQHNFQPSUTNCKW64%2F&h=8ecef9a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200817/QIT6AHBRJBGQHNFQPSUTNCKW64/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n測掌欠準 無人看守 <br />\n街市探熱器虛設<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】第三波武漢肺炎疫潮，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/a1t921SNJBOpCmc2ekTlzuvzg6Y=/2100x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LDMJCXVM7RABXPEELI7RVPYZVQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fa1t921SNJBOpCmc2ekTlzuvzg6Y%3D%2F2100x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLDMJCXVM7RABXPEELI7RVPYZVQ.jpg&h=740cf8d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【慈雲山中心】■有街坊在人臉辨識探熱機前多次移動頭部未能成功探熱，最終將手掌遞向探熱機。<br />\n<br />\n本報記者8月7日及8月12日到訪多個領展旗下商場及街市，了解探熱機作用。在樂富街市，領展職員並非要求進入街市人士透過額探量度體溫，而是建議他們伸出手掌，量度掌心溫度。感染及傳染病科醫生曾祈殷指出， 透過皮膚表面量度體溫不太準確，因皮膚表面容易受周邊環境影響，而影響探熱結果。記者先後拿着熱飲及凍飲後實測，透過手掌量度體溫，發現體溫由36.8&deg;C，分別改變至39.3&deg;C及36.2&deg;C，可見手掌溫度易受影響。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/UA9cCsb0AnFOmRhLYGhNmpHyVi0=/1496x945/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/64HGDHKUHVDN7GY53JST2PQZZI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FUA9cCsb0AnFOmRhLYGhNmpHyVi0%3D%2F1496x945%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F64HGDHKUHVDN7GY53JST2PQZZI.jpg&h=fafe00e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n額探機距離太遠<br />\n<br />\n在疫症個案眾多的慈雲山，領展在慈雲山中心加裝了探熱機，但與一般街市款式不相同，而是人面識別探熱機。記者嘗試探熱後進入商場，發現探熱機與被量體溫者距離甚遠，曾祈殷指出， 一般額探需將探熱儀器，放在眉心對上距離一至兩厘米的地方，如探熱器與額頭相距超過6厘米，結果已不準確。<br />\n<br />\n記者亦發現，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n領展回覆稱，探熱機優先安裝在疫情嚴重地區。對於慈雲山中心的人面識別探熱機，領展表示供應商稱可在較遠情況下準確量度體溫，同時亦可監測訪客有否戴上口罩。至於其他街市所設的紅外線探熱機，因應外界關注透過手掌量度體溫的準確度，已要求職員建議訪客以額頭探熱。對於部份街市的探熱機並無職員看守，領展已建議相關街市承租商完善有關安排。"},{"pid":"16fe18ec18d63e9da78e2e5f5d2e05766c4c0f4b","tid":2160408,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T02:41:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpzQVKm0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpzQVKm0.jpg&h=80fb0f7d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"883191e7858df38009fc0adcf0a2725afbac004b","tid":2160408,"uid":65638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T02:41:26.000Z","msg":"習近平都係量手掌啦<br />\n係咪想暗示話佢唔得<br />\n想破壞國家安全？"},{"pid":"ab1d5385a3e5f0d70448aba4e40aae8842aafb40","tid":2160408,"uid":297045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T02:42:44.000Z","msg":"好心唔好搞咁多野啦 再擴大依D機構既權力<br />\n探咩野熱呀 探完熱證明佢發燒 唔通即刻拉佢去隔離咩"},{"pid":"2a7a79054d353d4dfd6ed96ea387ea426fb9e838","tid":2160408,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T02:42:48.000Z","msg":"額頭一樣可以求其搽少少酒精上去就凍晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"700b5c1a45b6a9ca76d39342e5914096b9f7fd52","tid":2160408,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T02:42:57.000Z","msg":"嗰啲支那產品係咁上下"},{"pid":"bc368387e6ee514e7730d64585c3316dc54e749b","tid":2160408,"uid":14918,"like"